                              (s. <locus target="#37r">37r-</locus>v)</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the donors in supplication
                           formulas; headings and incipits of the texts; directives for the
                           ministers; most of the abbreviations; elements of the punctuation signs;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals; Additio I.</seg>
                     </handNote>
