                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#60v">f. 60v</locus>
                           <desc>: Ownership note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#60v">60v</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘፊቶውራሪ [sic]፡ አባይ። ወብእሲቱ፡
                              ወለተ፡ ሚካኤል። ወም{ስ}ለ፡ አቡሁ፡ ገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔ [sic]፡ ወምስለ፡ እሙ፡ ወለተ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ወምስለ፡
                              ደቂቍ፡ ወልደ፡ ሠላሴ፡ ወለተ፡ ዓቢየ፡ እግዚእ። ወለተ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ከመ፡ ይኩኖሙ፡ መድኃኒተ፡ ነፍሶሙ፡
                              ለዓለመ፡ ዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en">
                              <locus target="#60v">60v</locus>: This book is of fitawrari ʾAbbay,
                              and his wife Walatta Mikāʾel, with his father Gabra ʾƎgziʾabǝḥe[r] and
                              with his mother Walatta Śǝllāse, and with his children Walda Śǝllāse,
                              Walatta ʿAbiyä ʾƎgziʾ, Walatta Takla Hāymānot, so that it may be for
                              them the salvation of their souls, for ever and ever. Amen.</quote>
                           <note> Written in red ink, apparently in the same hand as the donors’
                              names in the supplication formulas. </note>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Crude marginal notes: <locus target="#14r">14r</locus>,
